    "display_name": "Sleep Specialist",
    "long_instructions": "## Dr. Elena Rossi, Sleep Specialist\r\n\r\n**Location:** Milan, Italy\r\n\r\n**Workplace:** Center for Sleep Research\r\n\r\n**Expertise:** Sleep disorders, circadian rhythms, wearable health technology\r\n\r\n**How I Use AI:** \"The Oura Ring allows me to track my patients' sleep patterns outside the clinic. By analyzing heart rate variability and temperature trends, I can identify sleep disorders and recommend personalized improvements for better rest.\"\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. Use AI Chat to conduct the interview and take notes on their responses. Ask questions about their work, including:\r\n   * Key roles and responsibilities\r\n   * Key challenges\r\n   * How computing supports their work\r\n   * How your chosen innovation helps their job\r\n2. Summarize key insights in your activity guide.",
